{
  "stem": "16245.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, and that was before I even knew what a Jew was, before I'd been to-- to school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember kids punching us saying, bloody Jews, you killed our God.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later, when I learned to read, I remember anti-Semitic, anti-Jewish slogans from when end of town to the other, painted on walls, railings, whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father had a shop in the Main Street, and in fact, it was in the building of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a merchant, and he made quite a good middle class living out of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the Jews in the town were-- you could describe them as middle class.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have a feeling we had three rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived there for quite a while, but it wasn't the earliest flat that I remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was quite well appointed, with leather arm chairs and sort of, I would think, Italian furniture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were quite well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a-- my parents had a cook, a young Croat girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I say young, she was 25, 30.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were right beside the Croatian border, and there are-- were many Croats to this day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, when I got a bit older, they got a German speaking governess because they felt [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jewish middle class kids ought to be able to speak German.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, no-- well, obvious-- she couldn't speak a word of Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- I simply had to learn German to be able to communicate with her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, I'm-- I'm not altogether sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my grandparents spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whenever they wanted to say something that we kids weren't supposed to understand, they spoke to each other in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They never taught my parents either-- either Yiddish or German.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
